00:06:52,814 --> 00:06:54,613
Ti-so.

100
00:06:54,614 --> 00:06:57,513
"Kyosuke Haga (32), Choichiro's nephew" -Oops, I went flat on "ti".

101
00:06:57,514 --> 00:07:00,913
Sorry, an ambulance just went by.

102
00:07:00,914 --> 00:07:03,313
About yesterday's music,

103
00:07:03,314 --> 00:07:07,613
