233
00:13:53,128 --> 00:13:55,528
Fire! Open the curtains and look!

234
00:13:59,028 --> 00:14:00,727
Where's your uncle's room?

235
00:14:00,728 --> 00:14:03,528
It's on the 2nd floor right up the stairs.

236
00:14:05,428 --> 00:14:07,627
Hey, uncle, can you hear me?

237
00:14:07,628 --> 00:14:08,628
Hey!

238
00:14:08,629 --> 00:14:11,427
Darn. The door is locked.

239
00:14:11,428 --> 00:14:13,428
