-Great Uncle! -Don't go inside!

241
00:14:25,028 --> 00:14:26,628
It is impossible to help him.

242
00:14:28,328 --> 00:14:30,627
Ayane. Ayane...

243
00:14:30,628 --> 00:14:31,728
Grandfather!

244
00:14:34,828 --> 00:14:37,927
